name: Paperino e gli antichi vasi unca

description: At last, a second helping of DC's hit webcomic series! Lee Wagstaff is the daughter of a black sharecropper in the Depression-era town of Charon, Mississippi. When Lily Westmoreland, her white playmate, is snatched by agents of an evil creature known as Bog, Lee's father is accused of kidnapping. Lee's only hope is to follow Lily's trail into a fantastic and frightening alternate world. Along the way she enlists the help of a benevolent, blues-singing swamp monster called Bayou. Together, Lee and Bayou trek across a hauntingly familiar Southern Neverland, confronting creatures both benign and malevolent, in an effort to rescue Lily and save Lee's father from being lynched.

name: Le spazioavventure di Topolino e Pippo

description: When three misfit friends from high school reunite after a string of bad luck in their personal lives, what is the first thing they do? Go off-roading, of course! Each one thinks that challenging Mother Nature is somehow going to fix whatever issues they're dealing with. That is if they ever get their Jeep out of the increasingly bizarre swamp that they are trapped in.

When three misfit friends from high school reunite after a string of bad luck in their personal lives, what is the first thing they do? Go off-roading, of course! Each one thinks that challenging Mother Nature is somehow going to fix whatever issues they're dealing with. That is if they ever get their Jeep out of the increasingly bizarre swamp that they are trapped in.

This original story is set in the New York Times-bestselling world of Jim Butcher's Dresden Files, and is scripted by Butcher himself! When the supernatural world goes out of control, there's only one man to call: Harry Dresden, the only professional wizard in the Chicago phonebook. Collecting the mini-series in its entirety, this PREVIEWS Exclusive trade paperback is limited to a print run of 2,500!

volume.name: Jim Butcher's The Dresden Files: Welcome to the Jungle

name: La settimana terribile di Paper Bat

description: The time is night, Trigon the Terrible has come to Earth through this corrupted daughter and laid waste to the entire planet. With Earth's heroes laid low, the lands itself a hellish nightmare; only one team stands between this most powerful of demons and universal conquest; the Teen Titans. But before they can even face Trigon, they will have to face; Raven.
name: The Terror of Trigon

volume.name: The New Teen Titans: The Terror of Trigon

A comic book released on Comic-Con of 2011. A limited edition and prequel to the TV Series. The prequel comic book was distributed to those attended the July 22 Lost Girl panel, which featured stars Anna Silk (Ghost Whisperer) and Emmanuelle Vaugier (Saw II) as well as executive producers Jay Firestone and Michelle Lovretta.
name: Prologue
Battle Annual 1981

description: Aspen Matthews is back once again! But now, Aspen must deal with the global ramifications of the Blue and Black's exposure to the rest of the world. However, this is an Aspen that is through being manipulated by the outside forces surrounding her life. It's a brave new world for her and the rest of the cast of FATHOM, as they must attempt to piece together the fragments of a world shattered by the knowledge of their existence.
name: The Detritus Rising

description: After freeing Lord Kaai and the Princess Panduu from the dungeon prison in Irisius, Jack Natari and his companions escape into the wasteland. Once they reach safety near the citadel of Xiar, they encounter a new threat as they face the woman from Iltharra and her band of thieves in the desert Vastness of Blask.
name: The Woman from Iltharra

person_credits.name: Mark Nasso
person_credits.role: writer, editor, artist, penciler, letterer, inker, cover, production

description: The "Necronomicon" was always believed a powerful magical text written by Abdul Alhazred . Even more widespread is the belief that the book and his story are , in fact , literary inventions of the American writer Howard Phillips Lovecraft . Martin Mystere learns that the "Necronomicon " really exists, and that is not a book , but a mysterious movie that shows different images each time it is projected ...
name: Necronomicon

description: An ancient threat, remained dormant for millennia, is awakened and unleashes a wave of destructive madness generated by "sigma wave" radiation that can amplify the sensory perceptions leading to hallucinatory visions. It's up to the Detective of the Impossible, along with Java and scientist friend Bernard Kneale, to resolve the situation.
name: La macchina della follia

description: For the five hundredth anniversary of the discovery of America, Martin Mystere is involved in an affair that reaffirms how things went in a different way from that handed down by the "official" history. Through Angie, Martin knows a self-styled descendant of Christopher Columbus, who claims to have inherited from him a diary which states that the journey to the New World in 1492 was by no means the first. But while Mystere seeks the truth, a murderous fanatic does everything to keep it hidden.
name: La Quarta Caravella

description: "Operation Valhalla " was the code name of a Nazi plan to make use of "magical" weapons, one of which is still active: the " Vril " , a sort of elixir of life , responsible during the Second world War of the creation of an army of invincible soldiers who, today , could conquer the world.
name: L'ultimo mistero

description: The Yahi were a tribe of Native Americans. The last representative of this people , believed to be extinct , was found in 1911 and died in 1919 . Nowadays , the Yahi mysteriously reappear in thousands : they are , are peaceful , asking for help , understanding and protection. Their appearance sets off a real wave of fanaticism in the entire U.S. population . A hysteria that Martin and Java do not share...
name: La grande illusione

description: Jazan visits the carnival with his mother, and is instantly fascinated by it. His mother and him enter an airplane. the plane runs into foul weather and crashes. Jazan is the only survivor. The next years Jazan grows up with a pair of tiger cubs, being orphaned when a hunter killed their mother, becoming more like them, and they more like him. Being tracked down by the Hunter, Jazan is fated to run into that same carnival from so many years ago.
name: Welcome To The Show

description: XII century: the diary of a caravan on the Salt Road tells of a sinister Black Town located in the Sahara, but no map shows it. Here, many men of the caravan have mysteriously found the death and it is here that the Detective of the Impossible wants to get, using a strange star chart. An adventure in which Martin will face once again with the Men in Black and ancient links are proven between African desert and Australia.
name: La maledizione del Sahara

description: The most powerful criminal organizations , tight in a sinister alliance, have implemented a form of blackmail on a global scale : if not satisfied for their thirst of power, nine satellites armed with nuclear warheads will wipe out many cities around the world. Meanwhile , a group of people from all over the world, including Martin Mystère , are "called " in the Australian desert by the vision of a tree: the Tree of Life , perhaps the only force that can avert the terrible danger that threatens the whole world.
name: L’albero della vita

description: Martin Mystère and Sergej Orloff, together again, but this time by allies, move at a time to Iceland, "the island of ice and fire" in the footsteps of St. Brendan, the Irish monk. To guide them is a mysterious shield runic, left in America by the Vikings a thousand years before. In their research, the two former enemies retrace the path of Siegfried, the legendary dragon-slayer of the Nordic myths...
name: L'isola di ghiaccio e di fuoco
Il segreto degli Anasazi
La strega della Sierra
Segnali di fumo
Sangue Apache
Furia selvaggia
La locanda degli impiccati

description: The Hit List Agenda' heats up for Executive Assistant: Violet! England takes center stage in "The Hit List Agenda" as one man, Henry Vincent, the heir to the Velchem fortune, decides to protect his wealthy corporate interests--as well as his life-with force. Executive Assistant: Violet is the solution. However, when the events of his father's death become clear, and the crisis surrounding Vincent's various holdings begin to reach a boiling point across the globe, Violet must prove she has what it takes to protect their future while also confronting the demons within!
name: Sons and Daughters

description: The only thing you have to fear is...FEAR ITSELF! Starting in April, Marvel lifts the lid on a plot that might undo the Heroic Age just as it's getting started - with a universe-shattering attack from an unexpected quarter! In this issue of SPOTLIGHT, we dig deep with the creators behind FEAR ITSELF, including Matt Fraction (THOR, UNCANNY X-MEN) and Stuart Immonen (NEW AVENGERS) as they provide insight into the main event and the characters most affected by it! Plus: Take a look back at some of Marvel's biggest blockbusters through the years - from old-school epics like the Avengers/Defenders War and SECRET WARS to contemporary crossovers like CIVIL WAR and SIEGE!
name: Fear Itself: Spotlight

description: After last issue's momentous tussle of giants, it's now painfully clear that Armageddon has descended on the human race. The government's bungled attempts to thwart the giant monsters have left an infrastructure in ruin and a nomad society desperately struggling to survive. And also... GIANT MONSTER FIGHTS! Destruction abounds in this issue of Godzilla: Kingdom of Monsters, featuring new artist Victor Dos Santos!

DC Retroactive is an exciting event honoring the defining eras of DC's core heroes, featuring an original story by the legendary writers and artists who helped mold the characters! The 1970s were a time of spacefaring thrills for the Emerald Knight! Now, writer Dennis O'Neil returns to the character for a brand-new epic starring Hal Jordan! Plus: Following the 26-page lead story is a classic tale originally published in the '70s, also written by Dennis O'Neil!
name: Nightmare Planet; No Evil Shall Escape My Sight!
Liberty Sam
La nave negriera

description: Aspen’s first ever intra-series summer event, “The Hit List Agenda” debuts right HERE in the pages of this exciting first issue! The turmoil in South Asia erupts into chaos as “The Hit List Agenda” sets its sights on the Republic of India. Amidst the bloodshed of a devastating attack on the Israeli Embassy, one woman’s actions will force the government’s hand in inching towards a potential war with a rival nuclear superpower—Executive Assistant Lotus! Yet, the catastrophic national conflict she has set into motion by her exploits is nothing compared to the life-altering conflict rising inside her due to the misdeeds of her past!
name: Penitence

description: Invincible continues making up for lost time while he was out in space fighting The Viltrumite War. His efforts bring him face-to-face with PowerPlex, who still blames Invincible for the death of his wife and son. The thing is, these days Invincible has plenty to be angry about as well, so things are about to get intense!

'FIVE FUNERALS AND A BUCKET OF BLOOD' Part Three This issue: More of the SAME! What? The SAME?! Yes, the SAME level of over-the-top action-comedy, banter and monster-mashy goodness that's made SKULLKICKERS a creator-owned hit. You want more than that? Okay, here goes: love potions, plant monsters, murdering fae folk and a dead ape. Buy it!
name: Five Funerals & a Bucket Of Blood Part Three

description: The Tablets of Fate have been stolen. Lord Ao, creator and ruler of the gods, is furious. And the Earth will be made to suffer the price of his rage as he banishes the gods to the realm of humans and elves in the latest of the DC/TSR comics line, AVATAR. The gods will stop at nothing to recover the stolen relics and appease Lord Ao's anger...and the gods help any human (or other being) who gets in their way.
name: Shadowdale

description: Elminster the Sage is lost in the labyrinthine folds of magical chaos as the Realms quake in crisis...and Midnight, Adon and company stand trial for Elminster's murder.
name: Tantras

description: With the first Tablet of Fate in their possession, Midnight and her allies must now find the second Tablet in Waterdeep's City of Splendors before Cyric or Myrkul, god of the Dead, find it and use it for their own malevolent ends.
name: Waterdeep

description: In the now-grand tradition of the über-successful Ultimate Spider-Man #100 Project, Hulk 100 Project, and Wolverine: Weapon X Project, the Hero Initiative assembles the Avengers! All of Hero's 100+ original covers to Marvel Comics' New Avengers #1 are on display in this great book.
name: The New Avengers 100 Project

description: The Midnight Swan is on the loose! The Wanderer has reached Earth! The Godrealms are opened, the Lightning Lady is freed, and dark alliances are formed that even Silver Star and Galaxy Green may not be able to stand against. And in the middle of all this, one young man searches for his lost friend -- only to run afoul of Thunderfoot, the Half-Human. The explosion of cosmic wonder and unbridled adventure ramps up, as Kirby: Genesis continues! Also featuring Captain Victory, Dragonsbane and the Mythics, the Pioneer Two and more!
name: The Unknown Lands

description: Wolverine, Deadpool and a 15-Foot-Killer Robot walk down the street. Wolverine and Deadpool walk into a bar. The 15-Foot-Killer Robot ducks. He still hits his head. Now buy this book.

The 'Trickster God' story arc concludes in this issue as we find the last of our heroes headed for certain death. The Skeleton Man with the mighty Hammer held tightly in his fists and fueled by the loss of everyone he has ever loved, sets off to kill the god that caused him so much pain. Raven Hex, bound and tortured by Loki, reaches her mental breaking point and shatters.

At Black Rose Manor Raven Hex is bound by Loki and is being tormented with overwhelming sensations of pleasure. Suspended upside down the trickster god uses his thoughts to induce wave after wave of ecstasy into the helpless Raven urging her to submit to him and be his mistress.

Finally Raven can take it no more and submits, crying out that she will be his mistress, Loki releases her and she drops to the floor. Taunting her Loki makes her repeat it louder and louder then commands her to crawl to him. Raven crawls on her hands and knees across the floor to her new master who orders her to lick his boot. As Raven leans in bringing her tongue to the black boot of her new god she rebels and blasts him with and energy wave of magic.

As she continues to punish Loki under her spells Jon burst in to her rescue, momentarily distracted, Loki gets the upper hand and blasts Raven Hex with all his powers disintegrating her as she calls out with her dying breath to her dead father, “Your little girl comes to you! Hold me.. in your arms… once more.”

Jon now stands over the ashes of Ravens body, having seen the entire family of witches killed in just the last few hours. Loki muses that Raven was nothing but a passing fancy and demands Mjollnir. Jon wastes no time in unleashing the power of Thor’s hammer and blasts Loki with a beam of energy sending him through the wall. The trickster god returns with his golden spear and the two do battle destroying the Black Rose Manor.

Just as Loki is about to strike the killing blow, Jon bloodied and broken in the rubble, laughs at Loki telling him his boots are untied. Falling for the deception Loki looks down only to realize his boots don’t even have laces, but this has given Skeleton Man the seconds he needed to regain the initiative. He tosses the mighty hammer and strikes Loki in the chin with all the power of Mjollnir. The enchanted hammer returns to his hand and he stands over Loki’s body raising it to strike the final blow and kill the god.

Just then he is interrupted by Hel, the goddess of the underworld who begs him to stop, saying it is not Loki’s time to die. Jon tells her Loki has cost him everything he loves and speaking for all of mankind he no longer cares about the will of the gods. “You don’t listen to our prayers, maybe you will hear this.” He strikes don’t towards the unconscious Loki’s head with Mjollnir…

And then all is returned to the way it was, Jon is in the forgotten graveyard yelling at the troublesome occupants. His home still intact as though the events of the past night had not even happened.

The issue and the story arc “The Trickster God” concludes, and it is assumed that Hel, or another god, heard Jon’s cries and returned everything to the way it was in order to save Loki or to give back to the mortals below them.
name: The Trickster God, Part Four: The Hammer
